Aim: To create an XML file to store the student details and use stylesheet to displaying the browser. 

Program 
Studentdetails.xml 
 
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> 
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" href="Rule.css"?> 
<studentdetails> 
    <heading>Student Personal Details </heading> 
    <student> 
